text: Cazuo Matsumoto (born August 2, 1985) is a Brazilian table tennis player. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics as part of the Brazilian team in the men's team event. ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian male table tennis players Category:Brazilian people of Japanese descent Category:Olympic table tennis players of Brazil Category:Table tennis players at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:South American Games gold medalists for Brazil Category:South American Games silver medalists for Brazil Category:South American Games medalists in table tennis Category:Competitors at the 2006 South American Games
